                  <li><b>Calibration now works for explicit-content categories</b> — calibrates against the category's captions on-device when no positive sample images are available, instead of failing.</li>
                  <li><b>Fixed:</b> Applying a calibrated threshold no longer re-prompts for Screen Recording when it's already granted.</li>
